  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The slayer builds resistance to certain poisons over time. Each time he chooses this talent, he chooses one ability score. He gains a +4 bonus on saving throws against poisons that deal damage to the chosen ability score. The slayer can choose this talent multiple times. Each time he does, he chooses a new ability score and gains the bonus on saves against poisons that target that ability.</p>\n<p>The slayer must be at least 4th level and have the poison use talent to select this talent.</p>",
